(25, 'Vashti Crepe Croptop-Sharara Set', 'vashti-crepe-croptop-sharara-set', '<p>Vashti Crepe Croptop-Sharara Set.&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">Say hello to the \"Vashti Crepe Croptop-Sharara Set\" - a unique ensemble that effortlessly blends comfort and fashion, making a statement that\'s daring and delightful. Step up your ethnic fashion game with this one-of-a-kind set, perfect for all your festivities, weddings, and cultural events.<br></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">With regards to shipping, we work with the best of delivery partners such DTDC, DHL etc and your packages are handled by safe and reliable partners.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">SHIPPING POLICY FOR DOMESTIC ORDERS –</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">Shopzters offers “FREE SHIPPING” for orders within India above INR 1000. For&nbsp;order value below INR 1000, we charge a domestic shipping fee of INR 100.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">As in the case of orders from remote areas, the carriers may charge on a different basis. In such cases, the customers will be informed well in advance of the same.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">SHIPPING POLICY FOR INTERNATIONAL ORDERS –</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">We ship world wide and our international delivery charges are affordable. Please find the exact shipping prices while checkout. In case of doubts, please send us a mail to shop@shopzters.com and one of our customer service executives will be in touch with you shortly regarding international shipping charges.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">For most clothing orders, we take anywhere between 12 – 15 working days to dispatch as most of our products are custom made and for jewellery orders, it will mostly take 3 -12 working days to dispatch. The shipping details for the products are mentioned in respective product pages. Please refer to them.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 12000.00, 15000.00, 6, 21, 14, 'Yes', 'sku-25', 'barcode-25', 'Yes', 1, 1, '2025-08-19 05:06:55', '2026-02-18 11:33:49'),
(26, 'Meenadar Handloom Banarasi Silk Saree', 'meenadar-handloom-banarasi-silk-saree', '<p>Gungun Uprari &amp; Alkananda Bodapatty in Meenadar Handloom Banarasi Silk Saree</p>', 'Meenadar Handloom Banarasi Silk Saree', NULL, '13,109', 750.00, 800.00, 6, 21, 15, 'Yes', 'sku-26', 'barcode-26', 'Yes', 9, 1, '2025-08-19 05:13:12', '2026-02-25 10:00:20'),
(27, 'Olive Green Chiniya Silk Suit Set with Tie-Dye Marine Motifs', 'olive-green-chiniya-silk-suit-set-with-tie-dye-marine-motifs', '<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; color: rgb(49, 47, 47); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(254, 244, 238);\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 700;\">Key Features:</span><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">• Material: Handloom Chiniya Silk<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">• Color: Olive Green<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">• Kurta: Length Approx. 45 inches Tie-Dye Marine Motifs with Mirror and Hand Embellishments<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">• Pants: Length Approx. 40 inches Matching Straight Pants<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">• Dupatta: Bandhani Printed Organza Silk with Handcrafted Lace Borders</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; color: rgb(49, 47, 47); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(254, 244, 238);\">Deliver within 20-25 business days. For urgent delivery, please contact us.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 50000.00, 60000.00, 6, 21, 14, '', 'sku-27', 'barcode-27', 'Yes', 2, 1, '2025-08-19 05:22:26', '2026-02-25 11:53:51'),
(28, 'Red Marine Embroidered Chiniya Silk Suit Set', 'red-marine-embroidered-chiniya-silk-suit-set', '<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; color: rgb(49, 47, 47); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(254, 244, 238);\">Are you looking for a perfect balance of style and comfort in a suit? You are in the right place. Pick up this Red Marine Embroidered Chiniya Silk Suit Set that is a perfect fit for your wardrobe. Designed in a quality Chiniya silk fabric, it assures a soft and soothing touch against the skin. It has tie and dye kantha embroidered marine motifs on the border kurta and has round v neckline and 3/4th sleeves that comes with matching chiniya silk pants &amp; organza silk kantha embroidered dupatta. You can also team this suit set with a stole or contrast dupatta. Pair this with antique jewellery and chokers to look elegant.<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 7000.00, 8000.00, 6, 21, 14, 'Yes', 'sku-28', 'barcode-28', 'Yes', 6, 1, '2025-08-19 05:25:53', '2026-02-18 08:45:17'),
(29, 'New Pink Salwar Suit Dress', 'new-pink-salwar-suit-dress', 'New Pink Salwar Suit Dress', NULL, NULL, NULL, 5000.00, 6000.00, 6, 21, 16, 'Yes', 'sku-29', 'barcode-29', 'Yes', 0, 1, '2025-08-20 05:21:06', '2026-02-21 09:17:30'),
(30, 'SHARAV Smart Watch for Mens', 'sharav-smart-watch-for-mens', '<p>SHARAV Smart Watch for Mens, Women, D20 Android Smartwatch Touch Screen Bluetooth Smart Watches for Android iOS Phones Wrist Phone Watch - Y68 Smart Watch (Black)</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 5000.00, 6500.00, 1, 24, 12, '', 'sku-30', 'barcode-30', 'Yes', 10, 1, '2025-08-19 06:18:41', '2025-09-02 03:52:41'),
(31, 'Bunaai Yellow Mirror Work Kurta Pants', 'bunaai-yellow-mirror-work-kurta-pants', 'qw', '<p>Bunaai Yellow Mirror Work Kurta Pants.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Archivo, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px;\">Embodying the happiness of a sunny day, this gorgeous Kurta Set is here to steal hearts. The bright yellow colour of the kurta is eye-catching and adds a pop of vibrant hue to your wardrobe, while the intricate mirror work adds an element of elegance and sophistication. The kurta is cut in a comfortable and flattering silhouette, making it suitable for both casual and formal events. The set also includes matching pants, which provide a comfortable and streamlined look. The beautiful and intricate mirror work is carefully handcrafted, adding a touch of artistry and uniqueness to this already stunning kurta set.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Archivo, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3px;\">Model height: 5.4ft</p><p data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Archivo, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3px;\">Fabric:<span data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px;\">&nbsp;Cotton Silk</span></p><p data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Archivo, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3px;\">Size: Refer to size chart. Model is wearing size Small.</span></p>', 'qw', '', 650.00, 850.00, 6, 21, 14, 'Yes', 'sku-31', 'barcode-31', 'Yes', 2, 1, '2025-08-28 00:12:16', '2026-02-26 09:06:12'),
(32, 'Purple Cotton Suit Set', 'purple-cotton-suit-set', '<p>Purple Cotton Suit Set.</p><p class=\"product-extra-note fw-3 fs-13 mb-0 font-italic text-justify\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Archivo, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;\"><span data-sheets-root=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px;\">Add a royal touch to your ethnic collection with the Purple Cotton Suit Set. Crafted in soft cotton, this Anarkali-style kurta features a classic round neck adorned with delicate lace detailing and three-quarter sleeves. Paired with matching pants and a coordinating dupatta, this elegant ensemble is perfect for festive occasions, family gatherings, and graceful daytime celebrations.</span></p><p class=\"product-extra-note fw-3 fs-13 mb-0 font-italic text-justify\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Archivo, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3px; font-style: normal; text-align: left;\">Model height: 5.6ft<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Archivo, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3px;\">Fabric: Cotton</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Archivo, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3px;\">Handcrafted in India</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: rgb(221, 221, 221) transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Archivo, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3px;\">Size: Refer to size chart. Model is wearing size Small.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 420.00, 650.00, 6, 21, 16, 'Yes', 'sku-32', 'barcode-32', 'No', NULL, 1, '2025-08-28 00:19:38', '2025-09-04 04:05:36');
