(38, 'Designer Sofa Set:- Modern', 'designer-sofa-set-moder', '<p>Designer Sofa Set:- Modern Art Antique 4 seaters Sectional Sofa (Sky Blue &amp; White)</p><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.3; color: rgb(0, 75, 136); font-size: 29px; font-family: system_ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.6px; word-break: break-word; text-decoration-line: underline; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\">Designer Sofa Set:- Modern Art Antique 4 seaters Sectional Sofa (Sky Blue &amp; White)</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 75, 136); font-family: system_ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.6px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\">GKW Retail is a platform for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://shop.gkwretail.com/\" title=\"Furniture Online\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(235, 70, 66); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">Furniture Online</span></a>&nbsp;that offers a wide range of gorgeous or premium&nbsp;<a href=\"https://shop.gkwretail.com/collections/sofa-set\" title=\"Sofa Set\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(235, 70, 66); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;Sofa Set</span></a>&nbsp;to assent all your needs as well as the furniture that complements your interiors.</p><div id=\"productDescription\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-small\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 75, 136); font-family: system_ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.6px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Constructed with a solid wood inner frame and upholstered in good-quality fabric, this&nbsp;<a href=\"https://shop.gkwretail.com/collections/fabric-sofa-set\" title=\"Fabric Sofa Set\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(235, 70, 66); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">Fabric Sofa Set</span></a><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;</span>has polyurethane cushioned backrest and seat. If your mood calls for it, the rest section can be located either on the left or right side of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://shop.gkwretail.com/collections/l-shape-sofa-set\" title=\"L Shape Sofa Set\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(235, 70, 66); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">L Shape Sofa Set</span></a>. With impeccable proportions and rich, solid base, this&nbsp;<a href=\"https://shop.gkwretail.com/collections/sectional-sofa-set\" title=\"Sectional Sofa Set\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(235, 70, 66); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">Sectional Sofa Set</span></a><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;</span>is a must-buy. Superior in every way, Go for this sofa set without giving a second thought to it!&nbsp;Acclaimed for its modern style and plush comfort,<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"https://shop.gkwretail.com/collections/designer-sofa-set\" title=\"Designer Sofa Set\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(235, 70, 66); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">Designer Sofa Set</span></a><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;</span>is gaining immense popularity in the market. With impeccable proportions and rich, solid base, this sofa<span data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;</span>is a must-buy. Superior in every way, Go for this sofa set without giving a second thought to it!&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">Dimension :-&nbsp;W x H x D: 137 cm x 83.82 cm x 137.16 cm (4 ft 5 in x 2 ft 9 in x 4 ft 6 in)</span></p></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 75, 136); font-family: system_ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.6px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\">Use: Living Room Sofa General Use: Home Furniture Mail packing: Y Application: Home Office, Living Room, Bedroom, Dining, Babies and kids, Hotel, School, Hotel Room .living Room. etc Design Style: Modern Material: Fabric Style: Corner Sofa Regional Style: European style Appearance: Modern Inflatable: No Type: Set Place of Origin: Guangdong, China Brand Name: GKW Retail Model Number: SFB5049 Feature: Fabric Product name: Office Sofa Usage: Living room Furniture MOQ: 1 Piece Function: Multi-purpose Packing: Carton Name: Modern European Use: Home Furniture Modern Sofa Design: Modern Design Color:&nbsp; Sky Blue.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 25000.00, NULL, 4, 19, 17, '', 'sku-39', 'barcode-39', 'Yes', 1, 1, '2025-09-01 04