(40, 'Fastrack Quartz Analog Silver Dial Silver', 'fastrack-quartz-analog-silver-dial-silver', '<p>Fastrack Quartz Analog Silver Dial Silver Stainless Steel Strap Watch for Guys - NS3039SM01</p><h3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: bold; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.255; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); margin-bottom: 6px !important;\">White Dial Analog</h3><h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini a-color-secondary\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.255; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 6px !important; color: rgb(86, 89, 89) !important;\">NG3039SM01C</h4><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">This analog watch for guys has plain three hands on a white, round dial with markings at five minutes intervals. The case is plain and silver in colour. This watch also comes with quartz movement, a back casing that is made of steel and a crown in order to adjust the time. Made of metal, the strap is silver in colour and has a deployment clasp for closure.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 600.00, NULL, 1, 24, 11, '', 'sku041', 'barcode-41', 'Yes', 6, 1, '2025-09-01 06:18:45', '2025-09-06 06:18:08');
