(57, 'Sonata Multifunction Green Dial Stainless Steel', 'sonata-multifunction-green-dial-stainless-steel', '<p>&nbsp;Sonata Wedding Multifunction Green Dial Stainless Steel Strap Watch For Men</p><ul class=\"text-justify\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.3125rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; line-height: 1.5rem; color: rgb(80, 93, 110); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; left: 0px !important;\">Step into your wedding day with distinguished style wearing the Wedding Multifunction green dial stainless steel strap watch for men. The rich green dial adds depth and character, while the multifunction features offer both practicality and elegance. The polished stainless steel strap enhances the watch\'s sleek design, perfectly complementing your wedding attire. More than just a timepiece, this watch symbolizes the commitment, strength, and timeless love that define your special day, serving as a lasting reminder of the beautiful journey you\'re starting together.</ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 6000.00, 8000.00, 1, 24, 10, '', 'sku-57', 'barcode-57', 'Yes', 12, 1, '2025-09-05 05:28:39', '2026-02-17 11:50:04'),
