(63, 'Apple MacBook Pro 14-inch M1 Max 64GB 2TB – Space Grey', 'apple-macbook-pro-14-inch-m1-max-64gb-2tb-space-grey', '<p>2021 Apple MacBook Pro 14-inch M1 Max 64GB 2TB – Space Grey</p><p style=\"--tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgb(59 130 246 / 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot;, &quot;dlig&quot;; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: aktiv-grotesk, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none !important;\">The 14-inch MacBook Pro M1 is one of the latest models of the MacBook Pro series, which Apple first introduced in 2006. The MacBook Pro has undergone several updates and revisions over the years, and the latest models feature the new M1 chip, which was first introduced in November 2020. The M1 chip is Apple\'s own custom-designed chip that offers faster performance and improved energy efficiency compared to the previous Intel-based models.</p><p style=\"--tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgb(59 130 246 / 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot;, &quot;dlig&quot;; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: aktiv-grotesk, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none !important;\">The 14-inch MacBook Pro M1 2021 is a high-performance laptop that perfectly balances power and portability. The M1 chip at the heart of this MacBook Pro is Apple\'s one of the latest and most potent chips to date, and it offers lightning-fast performance and efficiency. Starting with an 8-core CPU and 14-core GPU, and 16-core Neural Engine, this MacBook Pro can handle demanding tasks such as video editing, graphic design, and more. It also features a 14-inch Retina display with a resolution of 3924 x 1964, providing a stunning visual experience for watching videos, browsing photos, and working on documents.</p><p style=\"--tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgb(59 130 246 / 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot;, &quot;dlig&quot;; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: aktiv-grotesk, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none !important;\">The MacBook Pro M1 2021 features Touch ID allowing you to quickly log in to your MacBook Pro using your fingerprint, making it a secure and convenient way to unlock your device.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 4500.00, 5000.00, 1, 27, 18, '', 'sku-63', 'barcode-63', 'Yes', 5, 1, '2025-09-05 05:59:34', '2025-09-06 04:09:40'),
