(75, 'Puma Men\'s Lighter Indigo Slim Fit', 'puma-mens-lighter-indigo-slim-fit', '<p>Puma Men\'s Lighter Indigo Slim Fit</p><h3 class=\"text-uppercase Wrangler_Footer_Title\" style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-size: 18px; font-family: FuturaPTDemi;\">Jeans for Men</h3><p id=\"WranglerFooterText\" class=\"mt-3\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: FuturaPTBook;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">Wrangler jeans stand out as a classic choice for men\'s denim apparel, renowned for their exceptional quality and enduring style. As one of the leading brands in the industry, Wrangler has been synonymous with jeans for men for decades, consistently delivering on both comfort and durability. Crafted from premium denim fabric, Wrangler jeans offer a perfect blend of ruggedness and refinement, making them a staple in every man\'s wardrobe.</p><p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">From their iconic blue jeans for men to versatile denim pants in various fits and washes, Wrangler caters to the diverse needs and preferences of men everywhere. Whether you\'re looking for a timeless pair of denim jeans for casual wear or a more polished option for a night out, Wrangler\'s extensive range of men\'s jeans ensures there\'s a perfect fit for every occasion. With their timeless appeal and unwavering quality, Wrangler jeans continue to be the go-to choice for men seeking comfort, style, and reliability in their denim apparel.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 750.00, 800.00, 5, 22, 1, '', 'sku-75', 'barcode-3275', 'Yes', 4, 1, '2025-09-06 06:59:29', '2026-02-23 07:48:17'),
