(111, 'Puma Sports For Fit Girls Shooes', 'puma-sports-for-fit-girls-shooes', '<p style=\"outline: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">The sneakers have a rubber reinforced toe, which protects the toes and increases the durability of the shoes. Classic lacing allows for a perfect fit to the width of the leg, which translates into comfort of wearing. Set on a massive 3.5 cm platform, these sneakers not only add centimeters, but also provide stability during each step.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">Comfortable, material insole ensures foot comfort throughout the day. Ideal for everyday styling, they are perfect for spring, summer and autumn days. Thanks to minimalist design and subdued colors, sneakers are easy to match with various outfits.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">These women\'s sneakers come in a variety of sizes, so you can choose the right size. However, it\'s worth referring to the manufacturer\'s size chart to ensure a perfect fit.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">In conclusion, the PS1 Women\'s High Top Fabric Sneakers Blue are a great choice for any fashionable woman who wants to combine style with comfort. Regardless of the occasion, these sneakers are sure to attract attention and become a favorite item in your wardrobe.</p>', '<p>Puma Sports For Fit Girls Shooes</p>', '<p>nONo</p>', '', 250.00, NULL, 2, 17, 1, 'Yes', 'sku-111', 'barcode-111', 'Yes', 0, 1, '2025-09-15 06:07:44', '2026-02-19 07:25:50'),
