(117, 'Ladies Leather Office Shoes', 'ladies-leather-office-shoes', '<h2 class=\"sc-c6d82cff-0 sNMMF coy-details-title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-size: 20px; line-height: 28px; margin: 21px 0px 12px; font-weight: 700 !important;\">Company Details</h2><div class=\"sc-c6d82cff-0 hEKoFN overflow-x seo-content\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; overflow-x: auto;\">Vivek Manufacturer, Established in&nbsp;2016&nbsp;at Mumbai in Maharashtra, is a leading Manufacturer,Supplier of Leather Shoes in India. Vivek Manufacturer is one of Trade India\'s verified and trusted sellers of listed products. With extensive experience in supplying and trading Ladies Leather Office Shoes , Vivek Manufacturer has made a reputed name for itself in the market with high-quality Ladies Leather Office Shoes , Ladies Leather Shoes, Ladies Leather Shoes , etc.<br>Focusing on a customer-centric approach, Vivek Manufacturer has a pan-India presence and caters to a huge consumer base throughout the country. Buy Leather Shoes in bulk from Vivek Manufacturer at Trade India quality-assured products.</div>', '<h1 class=\"sc-c6d82cff-0 jxSRln product-title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(45, 56, 64); font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(210, 218, 224); font-weight: 700 !important;\">Ladies Leather Office Shoes</h1>', '<p>No</p>', '37,116', 200.00, 250.00, 2, 17, 9, 'Yes', 'sku-117', 'barcode-117', 'Yes', 0, 1, '2025-09-15 06:43:49', '2025-11-10 07:44:06'),
