(119, 'Men Blue Mid Wash Jeans', 'men-blue-mid-wash-jeans', '<p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 ProductDetails_heading__Coxvn css-12a9y8i\" style=\"margin: -7px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 11px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.31; font-family: Inter; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: uppercase;\">product description</p><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 ProductDetails_description__uJq4_ css-12a9y8i\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 11px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.67; font-family: Inter; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Enhance your casual outings with these refined blue jeans from Allen Solly. Meticulously designed using a premium cotton and spandex blend, they promise a comfortable fit that moves with you. The solid pattern complements a variety of styles, making them a versatile addition to any wardrobe. Ideal for relaxed gatherings or everyday wear, these jeans elevate your look with understated elegance, keeping you stylishly confident wherever your day takes you.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Inter; font-size: 12px;\">Enhance your casual outings with these refined blue jeans&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p>Yes</p>', '11,55', 3199.00, 3500.00, 5, 22, 9, 'Yes', 'sku-119', 'barcode-119', 'Yes', 0, 1, '2025-12-22 06:59:41', '2026-02-25 12:50:10'),
(120, 'Men Blue Slim Fit Light Wash Jeans', 'men-blue-slim-fit-light-wash-jeans', '<p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 ProductDetails_heading__Coxvn css-12a9y8i\" style=\"margin: -7px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 11px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.31; font-family: Inter; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: uppercase;\">product description</p><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 ProductDetails_description__uJq4_ css-12a9y8i\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 11px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.67; font-family: Inter; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Experience everyday sophistication with these Allen Solly jeans, where impeccable style meets unmatched comfort. The rich blue hue adds a contemporary flair, while the slim fit enhances your silhouette for a refined look. Finely crafted from a cotton-blend fabric, these jeans promise breathability and durability ideal for casual outings. Pair them effortlessly with a tee or a casual shirt to complete your ensemble. Elevate your leisurewear with this stylish staple.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Inter;