(121, 'DIY Feels Jeans', 'diy-feels-jeans', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-family: Jost, sans-serif;\">This is a one-off design. The jeans is hand embroidered. Final product may come out slightly different due to the nature of making process.</span></p><p style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgba(39, 39, 39, 0.12); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-family: Jost, sans-serif; margin-block-start: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgba(39, 39, 39, 0.12); font-weight: bolder; margin-block-start: 0px !important;\">If you have access to a measuring tape</span>, measure your true body chest in inches. Say your chest is 40in, for oversize fit -<br style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgba(39, 39, 39, 0.12); margin-block: 0px !important;\"></p><ul style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgba(39, 39, 39, 0.12); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inside; margin-block-start: 16px; row-gap: 0.6em; display: grid; color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-family: Jost, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgba(39, 39, 39, 0.12);\">Select size 46 in T-shirt, Shirt</li><li style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgba(39, 39, 39, 0.12);\">Select size 48 in Hoodie</li><li style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgba(39, 39, 39, 0.12);\">Select size 50 in Jacket<br style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgba(39, 39, 39, 0.12); margin-block: 0px !important;\"></li></ul><p style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgba(39, 39, 39, 0.12); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-block-start: 24px; color: rgb(39, 39, 39); font-family: Jost, sans-serif; margin-block-end: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"border-style: so